          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Overview",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Use this type to observe or customize the issue(s) recorded by the test this",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "trait is applied to. You can transform a recorded issue by copying it,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "modifying one or more of its properties, and returning the copy. You can",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "observe recorded issues by returning them unmodified. Or you can suppress an",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "issue by either filtering it using ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.testing\/documentation\/Testing\/Trait\/filterIssues(_:)",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " or returning",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "nil",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " from the closure passed to ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.testing\/documentation\/Testing\/Trait\/compactMapIssues(_:)",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "When an instance of this trait is applied to a suite, it is recursively",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "inherited by all child suites and tests.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "To add this trait to a test, use one of the following functions:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
